5 Punn tãnnim kan diunk na, ani eklo aplea bhattant, dusro aplea veapar-dhondeak gelo;
6 heramnim chakrank dhôrle, tankam boddoile ani tancho jiv kaddlo.
7 Hem aikun razacho rag pettlo ani aplim loskoram dhaddun tea khuniancho tannem bhosm kelo ani tanchem nogor lasun uddoilem.
8 Uprant tannem aplea chakrank sanglem: Lognachem jevonn tôr toiar asa, punn apoilleank tem favona zalem;
